/* eslint-disable import/no-unresolved */
import { Carousel } from "react-bootstrap"
import "bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
import React, { Component } from "react"
// import { ReactComponent as LocationSVG } from "./img/location.svg"
import "./styles/carousel_style.css"
import {
  SaleTitle,
  PackageTitle,
  Underline,
  // Location,
  Price,
  OldPrice,
  NewPrice,
  Button,
  Text,
  Image,
} from "./styles/carousel"

class ControlledCarousel extends Component {
  constructor(props) {
    super(props)
    this.state = {
      // eslint-disable-next-line
      index: 0,
    }
    this.handleSelect = this.handleSelect.bind(this)
  }

  handleSelect(selectedIndex) {
    // eslint-disable-next-line
    this.setState({ index: selectedIndex })
  }

  render() {
    return (
      <Carousel activeIndex={this.index} onSelect={this.handleSelect}>
        <Carousel.Item>
          <Carousel.Caption className="leftText">
            <SaleTitle>ON SALE</SaleTitle>
            <PackageTitle>
              BYRON BAY <Underline>EXPERIENCES</Underline>
            </PackageTitle>
            {/* <Location>
              <LocationSVG className="location-svg" />
              Sydney
            </Location> */}
            <Price>
              <OldPrice>$1200</OldPrice>
              <NewPrice>$600 per person</NewPrice>
            </Price>
            <Text>
              Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.
              Scelerisque velit laoreet sit vitae laoreet id purus a aliquam.
              Faucibus purus elementum at ullamcorper
            </Text>
            <Text>
              Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.
            </Text>
            <Button>Book now</Button>
          </Carousel.Caption>
          <Image
            className="d-block"
            src="/img/carousel/carousel-1.jpg"
            alt="slide"
          />
        </Carousel.Item>
        <Carousel.Item>
          <Carousel.Caption className="leftText">
            <SaleTitle>ON SALE</SaleTitle>
            <PackageTitle>
              BYRON BAY <Underline>EXPERIENCES</Underline>
            </PackageTitle>
            {/* <Location>
              <LocationSVG className="location-svg" />
              AUSTRALIA
            </Location> */}
            <Price>
              <OldPrice>$1200</OldPrice>
              <NewPrice>$600 / ppl</NewPrice>
            </Price>
            <Text>
              Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.
              Scelerisque velit laoreet sit vitae laoreet id purus a aliquam.
              Faucibus purus elementum at ullamcorper.
            </Text>
            <Text>
              Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.
            </Text>
            <Button>Book now</Button>
          </Carousel.Caption>
          <Image
            className="d-block"
            src="/img/carousel/carousel-2.jpg"
            alt="slide"
          />
        </Carousel.Item>
        <Carousel.Item>
          <Carousel.Caption className="leftText">
            <SaleTitle>ON SALE</SaleTitle>
            <PackageTitle>
              BYRON BAY <Underline>EXPERIENCES</Underline>
            </PackageTitle>
            {/* <Location>
              <LocationSVG className="location-svg" />
              AUSTRALIA
            </Location> */}
            <Price>
              <OldPrice>$1200</OldPrice>
              <NewPrice>$600 / ppl</NewPrice>
            </Price>
            <Text>
              Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.
              Scelerisque velit laoreet sit vitae laoreet id purus a aliquam.
              Faucibus purus elementum at ullamcorper.
            </Text>
            <Text>
              Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.
            </Text>
            <Button>Book now</Button>
          </Carousel.Caption>
          <Image
            className="d-block"
            src="/img/carousel/carousel-3.jpg"
            alt="slide"
          />
        </Carousel.Item>
      </Carousel>
    )
  }
}

export default ControlledCarousel
